item.description: About me Hey! My name is Fabian Grutsch and I am working as a Backend Engineer at Firstbird. At Firstbird we are building an SaaS referral platform with Scala, Akka, Playframework and AWS. Currently, I am living in my hometown which is based in Tyrol (Austria). As Firstbird has its HQ in Vienna (Austria) I am working for more than 3 years now from a Coworking Space.
